{"id":147026,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/泰柬边境战没有任何缓解的迹象/","date":"2011-04-24T02:30:14Z","modified":"2011-04-24T02:30:14Z","title":"泰柬边境战没有任何缓解的迹象","content":"<div>\n<p>泰国和柬埔寨的边境战没有任何缓解的迹象。周六，在双方持续了数小时的交火中，三名柬埔寨士兵和一名泰国士兵丧生。自周五以来被打死的士兵人数上升到10人。30多名士兵受伤。数千名泰国当地农民，因这场自2月以来爆发的最为激烈的战斗，不得不转移到安全地带。柬泰边境大约800公里地区中的大部分是主权争议地区。争执的焦点是柏威夏古寺。1962年海牙国际法庭裁决，柬埔寨拥有这座古寺。</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C6511546%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E6%B3%B0%E6%9F%AC%E8%BE%B9%E5%A2%83%E6%88%98%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%B9%E8%B1%A1\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}